      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows some noticeable wear, including several scuffs, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows clear signs of age with some staining on the upholstery and wear on the steering wheel. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind some cosmetic character.",
