      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and small door dings consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with all major systems functioning as intended and a consistent service history. It drives smoothly and represents a reliable option for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle without the price tag of a brand-new model.",
